rekit.logic.gameelements.entities.enemies.bosses.rocketboss.arm.armaction

Class ArmAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • rekit.logic.gameelements.entities.enemies.bosses.rocketboss.arm.RocketBossChild
      • rekit.logic.gameelements.entities.enemies.bosses.rocketboss.arm.armaction.ArmAction
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArmActionCannon, ArmActionRocketLauncher

    public abstract class ArmAction
extends RocketBossChild
    This abstract ArmAction represents what the RocketBoss can hold in its hand at the end of its Arm. The ArmAction is supplied with:
    • A perform() method that will be called once at a specific time
    • A periodic logicLoop(float calcX, float deltaX)-call
    • A periodic logicLoop(float, float)-call
    • A tearDown() method that will be called upon the ArmActions end.
    Author:
    Angelo Aracri
